OL,3,CMan who released rats outside mosque
OL,4,Cfour times avoids prison
OL,6,FA man who released rats near a mosque
OL,7,Fin a series of racist hate crimes has
OL,8,Favoided being sent to prison.
OL,10,FEdmund Fowler, 66, took wild rodents
OL,11,Fto Sheffield Grand Mosque on four
OL,12,Fseparate occasions between May and
OL,13,FJune.
OL,15,FIn CCTV footage captured outside the
OL,16,Fmosque he could be seen lifting a cage
OL,17,Ffrom the boot of his car before
OL,18,Ffreeing the animals onto the pavement.
