OL,3,CMan who released rats outside mosque
OL,4,Cfour times avoids prison
OL,6,FMobile phone footage filmed by Fowler
OL,7,Frecorded him talking to the rats,
OL,8,Fsaying "guess where you're going",
OL,9,F"say bye bye" and "I'll point you in
OL,10,Fthe right direction".
OL,12,FFowler, of Skelwith Drive, Sheffield,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to four counts of
OL,14,Fracially aggravated harassment at
OL,15,FSheffield Magistrates' Court.
OL,17,FAn anti-hate crime charity said the
OL,18,Fincident was "highly dehumanising".
