OL,3,CMan who released rats outside mosque
OL,4,Cfour times avoids prison
OL,6,FFowler was sentenced to 18 weeks in
OL,7,Fprison, suspended for 18 months, and
OL,8,Fbanned from going near a mosque and to
OL,9,Fcertain parts of the city for 18
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FThe CCTV footage played in court
OL,13,Fshowed Fowler parking his Audi near
OL,14,Fthe mosque on Grimesthorpe Road and
OL,15,Fshouting racist insults at people
OL,16,Fentering the building.
OL,18,FHe had caused widespread "upset and
OL,19,Fshock" within the community, the court
OL,20,Fheard.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
