OL,3,CMan who released rats outside mosque
OL,4,Cfour times avoids prison
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,7,Fmosque manager said: "It is evident
OL,8,Fpeople using the mosque are Muslim.
OL,10,F"They are scared of further harassment
OL,11,Fand are now too scared to come to the
OL,12,Fmosque."
OL,14,FThe court heard Fowler accepted his
OL,15,Fbehaviour was "appalling" but gave no
OL,16,Fmotive.
OL,18,FHe may have had a mental breakdown as
OL,19,Fa result of the pressures of caring
OL,20,Ffor his wife, who has breast cancer,
OL,21,Fthe court was told.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
