OL,3,CMan who released rats outside mosque
OL,4,Cfour times avoids prison
OL,6,FChair of the bench, Suzanne Irish-
OL,7,FDeverill, told Fowler she was
OL,8,F"disgusted" by the footage and that
OL,9,Fhis crimes were "pre-planned on
OL,10,Fmultiple occasions".
OL,12,FShe added: "You also had the audacity
OL,13,Fto record it yourself. It has had
OL,14,Fsignificant impact and caused shock
OL,15,Fand distress.
OL,17,F"People are entitled to travel to a
OL,18,Fplace of worship without being
OL,19,Fracially or religiously harassed - it
OL,20,Fis a hate crime."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
